yKmtSHb0KjtU5f2M6j3-vFGoIYfgt8JTA34GnQP2M1MUuaTGsSgPU4t5RZg7EfU89XMKHJ_lfs2IReRe6J39zV6FgTsJl_DlYd5DteNh_j2LF86sWO9BudckkDrcsBs3RXkF0muyp7eNNX0vSbG4iUASg1CM4FCI7zVff9IBQSSNQzCrTLuAdawkgCDiE5eyuqRGq8DOmCp\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Inspecting build conditions**\\n\\nI’m looking into a problem with the native run failing in existing tests. Adding an optional dependency might complicate things and increase metadata, which isn’t ideal. It’s also worth noting that our local server isn't using Docker. I should check the documentation to understand how the web client interacts with the server. There may be issues with the current test run from version 5.0.0, especially with the environment settings. I'll examine the failing stack next.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"action\": \"advisory_preparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"No extra Maven dependency or Docker service is needed for meaningful Vert.x Web Client coverage, but Vert.x 5.0.1 still resolves Netty 4.2.x and needs the same JDK 25 native runtime properties already documented for 5.0.0.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Use self-hosted Vert.x HTTP servers in the tests for WebClient, CachingWebClient, WebClientSession, JSON/form/multipart, redirects, and streaming coverage; no external service is required. For native-image run tests on JDK 25, ensure the generated test project applies the Netty runtime/system properties `-Dsun.misc.unsafe.memory.access=allow` and `-Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true` for vertx-web-client 5.0.1 as well, e.g. by broadening the existing Vert.x 5.0.x/Netty 4.2.x condition rather than leaving it pinned to 5.0.0.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The public OAuth2WebClient API references the optional `io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2` module; avoid OAuth2-specific tests unless deliberately adding that optional dependency.\",\n    \"Netty native/JDK 25 behavior is version-sensitive, so local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0890bf1f7e9b02ec016a3e87b5f5908190aa2f6faf40ef581d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1278, "output": 1286, "cacheRead": 41984, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 44548, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782482855222, "responseId": "resp_0890bf1f7e9b02ec016a3e87a7b0808190b77c713227a637ed"}, "toolResults": []}
